'''Asif n Masst''' iga yan wasif illan ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], tiɣzi nns tlkm 120 km. Ar itffi wasif ad ɣ yat lblast taggug s kran mraw ikilumitren f tagrawt n [[Massa]] nna ɣ yusi nit ism nns. Amda nns illa ɣ iffus n tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Masst|Sus-Masst]] nna ɣ tlla [[Sus]] ɣ ugafa d wasif n Massa ɣ iffus nns.

== Tarakal ==
Yaggug wasif ad f tiɣrmt n [[Agadir|Ugadir]] s 50 km ɣ iffus nns, iqrrb ukan i yan udwar iga s yism Sidi Rbat, ɣ tamnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Wactukn-Ayt Baha]] ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]], Ar itffi wasif ad ɣ [[Ill Aṭlasi|yill Aṭlasi]].

